			"body": "<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: summarize by coderabbit.ai -->\n<!-- walkthrough_start -->\n\n<details>\n<summary>📝 Walkthrough</summary>\n\n## Walkthrough\n\nA new \"What's New\" dialog has been introduced to display release notes and media when desktop app updates are available. The update checking flow has been modified to dispatch dialog-open actions instead of relying solely on system dialogs, with utilities updated to extract media URLs from release bodies.\n\n## Changes\n\n|Cohort / File(s)|Summary|\n|---|---|\n|**Ignore configuration** <br> `.eslintignore`, `.gitignore`|Two WhatsNewDialog files added to ignore rules for linting and version control.|\n|**Update check flow** <br> `packages/app-desktop/app.ts`, `packages/app-desktop/checkForUpdates.ts`, `packages/app-desktop/gui/MenuBar.tsx`|Added optional dispatch callback parameter to checkForUpdates function. When dispatch is provided and a new release is available, a DIALOG_OPEN action is dispatched to display the what's new dialog instead of the native update prompt.|\n|**Notification and dialog components** <br> `packages/app-desktop/gui/UpdateNotification/UpdateNotification.tsx`, `packages/app-desktop/gui/WhatsNewDialog/ReleaseNotesSection.tsx`, `packages/app-desktop/gui/WhatsNewDialog/WhatsNewDialog.tsx`, `packages/app-desktop/gui/WindowCommandsAndDialogs/utils/appDialogs.tsx`|New ReleaseNotesSection and WhatsNewDialog components introduced to render release notes, media links, and download options. UpdateNotification updated to accept dispatch prop and conditionally render a \"What's New\" button. Dialog registry updated with whatsNew entry.|\n|**Update utilities** <br> `packages/app-desktop/utils/checkForUpdatesUtils.ts`, `packages/app-desktop/utils/checkForUpdatesUtils.test.ts`|Added extractMediaUrl function to parse media URLs (Twitter, YouTube) from release bodies. Release interface extended with optional mediaUrl field. extractVersionInfo updated to populate mediaUrl.|\n\n## Su